'''Bullion''' ni filime yerekana ikinamico yo muri [[Uganda]] 2014 yakozwe na Henry Ssali kandi iyobowe na Phillip Luswata<ref>Bullion Movie Premiere For April 5TH | Chano8 <nowiki>https://chano8.com</nowiki> › bullion-movie-premiere-for-april-...</ref>. Muri iyi filime hagaragaramo Allan Tumusiime, umukinnyi wa filime wo muri [[Kenya]] Ainea Ojiambo, umuririmbyi Juliana Kanyomozi na mushiki we Laura Kahunde<ref>Bullion (film) and similar films | Frankensaurus.com <nowiki>https://frankensaurus.com</nowiki> › Bullion_(film)</ref>, umunyamakuru wa radiyo na Veronica Tindi w’uruganda rushimishije [[Anne Kansiime|, umunyarwenya Anne Kansiime]], Michael Wawuyo n'umuhungu we Michael Wawuyo Jr. ndetse no kugaragara k'umunyamideli n'umucuruzi. Sylvia Owori<ref>Will BULLION MOVIE bring Uganda its first OSCAR AWARD? <nowiki>https://bigeye.ug</nowiki> › will-bullion-movie-bring-uganda-an...</ref> .  

== Incamake ==
Collins Jjuuko, umushoferi wimodoka ya bullion arashaka cyane amafaranga yo guha umukobwa we ugiye kubagwa umutima  mubuhinde<ref>Bullion arrives at last - Observer Ug <nowiki>https://observer.ug</nowiki> › component › content › article › id...</ref>. Yifatanije nitsinda ryabakozi ba banki bafite umururumba kwiba imodoka ya bullion. Nyuma y’ubwo bujura, bagenzi be bamutwara amafaranga yose nuko arafatwa<ref>'Bullion' premiere raises the bar | The Critic <nowiki>https://kamukamapolly.wordpress.com</nowiki> › 2014/04/08</ref>. Iyo avuye muri gereza, aba ashaka kwishyura<ref>Bullion Premieres Saturday - Uganda News Releases <nowiki>https://www.ugandanewsreleases.com</nowiki> › ﻿bullion-premier...</ref>. 

== Umusaruro na premiere ==
Filime yakozwe na Henry Ssali munsi ya Ssali Productions. Niyo filime ye ya kabiri yakoze nyuma yo gukora Kiwani muri 2008<ref>Uganda: Henry Ssali's Bullion May Be Here, Finally - allAfrica ... <nowiki>https://allafrica.com</nowiki> › stories</ref>. Yakozwe nubuyobozi  w'umutunzi n'umucuruzi Sudhir Ruparelia nawe wari umuyobozi mukuru yabyaye Kiwani. gutunganywa ndetse no gukina filimi  byatangiye mu 2009 mugihe amashusho yoherejwe hanze   muri 2014. Icyo gihe yerekanwe bwa mbere muri Mata 2014 i Munyonyo Kampala<ref>Bullion - Cultures-Uganda <nowiki>http://uganda.spla.pro</nowiki> › file.film.bullion.17050.html</ref>.  

=== Kasting ===
Igenzura ryabakinnyi ba film ryatangiye muri 2009. Allan Tumusiime, wigeze gukora kuri filime ya mbere ya Ssali Kiwani, yakinnye nka Collins Jjuuko. Umukinnyi  wa filimi muri [[Kenya]] Makutano Ainea Ojiambo yatowe nkumuntu wanyuze kuri Phillip Luswata nawe wakoraga kuri Makutano<ref>Kate Hutchinson with Bullion // 20-09-19 | WorldwideFM <nowiki>https://worldwidefm.net</nowiki> › episode › kate-hutchinson-with-...</ref>. Ssali kandi yateye umuririmbyi Juliana Kanyomozi wari watangiye umwuga we wo gukina filime ye ya mbere Kiwani.<ref>Bullion Van Song by bigBen | Back to J town Songs (2020) <nowiki>https://www.hungama.com</nowiki> › ... › Back to J town Songs</ref>
